headline: The Ultimate Growth Stock to Buy With $1,000 Right Now
summary: Investors can find exciting growth stocks set to soar even outside the tech sector.  Carnival has been posting record results on metrics from revenue to bookings.  When you think of growth stocks these days, you probably think of players in the technology sector, and specifically those that are exposed to the artificial intelligence (AI) trend.
